@startuml c4-jotp-04-process-lifecycle
title JOTP - Process Lifecycle Sequence Diagram

participant Developer
participant "ProcLib\n(startup)" as ProcLib
participant "Proc<S,M>\n(handler)" as Proc
participant "Supervisor" as Supervisor
participant "CrashRecovery" as Recovery
participant "ProcessRegistry" as Registry
participant "EventManager" as EventMgr

Developer ->> ProcLib: start_link(stateHandler)
activate ProcLib
ProcLib ->> Proc: new virtual thread\n+ mailbox
activate Proc
Proc ->> Proc: call stateHandler\ninitialize()
Proc ->> ProcLib: initAck(state)
deactivate Proc
ProcLib ->> Developer: return ProcRef
deactivate ProcLib

Developer ->> Registry: register("myproc", procRef)
activate Registry
Registry ->> Proc: tag process
deactivate Registry

Developer ->> Proc: send(message)
activate Proc
Proc ->> Proc: dequeue from mailbox\ncall stateHandler(state, msg)
Proc ->> Proc: nextState = handler result\nupdate state
deactivate Proc

note over Proc
  Process running normally
  Handling messages
  Transitioning state
end note

Developer ->> EventMgr: dispatch(event)
activate EventMgr
EventMgr ->> Proc: route event
activate Proc
Proc ->> Proc: StateMachine handles event\nstate/event/data dispatch
deactivate Proc
EventMgr ->> Developer: handler reply
deactivate EventMgr

Developer ->> Proc: crash or explicit stop
activate Proc
Proc ->> Proc: unhandled exception\nor exit signal
note over Proc
  Process crashes
end note
Proc ->> Supervisor: send ExitSignal
deactivate Proc
activate Supervisor

Supervisor ->> Supervisor: evaluate restart\nstrategy
Supervisor ->> Recovery: execute recovery\nwithin restart window

activate Recovery
Recovery ->> ProcLib: start_link()\n(restart)
activate ProcLib
ProcLib ->> Proc: spawn new process
activate Proc
Proc ->> Proc: reinitialize state
Proc ->> ProcLib: initAck(state)
deactivate Proc
ProcLib ->> Recovery: return new ProcRef
deactivate ProcLib
deactivate Recovery

Supervisor ->> Registry: update process reference
activate Registry
Registry ->> Registry: deregister old\nregister new
deactivate Registry

deactivate Supervisor

note over Proc
  Process restarted
  Same name, fresh state
end note

@enduml
